{"tid":974083,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"AIA 扔籃球 送條魚","createTime":"2019-01-08T15:21:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-08T15:27:56.000Z","uid":224777,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0dbfc8778cdaad5f31d5c03db5ddd1d30a108631","tid":974083,"uid":224777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T15:21:47.000Z","msg":"個日我同男朋友去左AIA <br />\n然後去左個個吾知邊檔既扔籃球 <br />\n個奬品係條魚 我記得我男朋友扔入左既時候 個個staff係個女仔黎 好鬼緊張 入吾到又好似好誇張咁話aiya好慘<br />\n本來諗住d staff咁用心 投入埋<br />\n但之後到比個獎品我地 個個staff 捉住我雙手同我講 <br />\n&lsquo;你吾好扔走條魚 要好好愛佢 佢會保佑你一生一世&rsquo;<br />\n我同我男朋友嚇親 吾知你地有無人去係咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"777ec6aa6611a48adb8c91e523d0433b1326470a","tid":974083,"uid":177561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T15:24:00.000Z","msg":"走啦, 吾唔想搞大佢"},{"pid":"bbde2246c1beb85d2bfba3da456ad53fbad4f4b2","tid":974083,"uid":3820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T15:24:34.000Z","msg":"55嗯"},{"pid":"7637569fee58b0c8f89a1eb602003eabcdc7e295","tid":974083,"uid":6098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T15:27:10.000Z","msg":"邊個係aiya?點慘法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f8091805218ab245b0bdfb06a910790de4414a6","tid":974083,"uid":28800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T15:27:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}